WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.640
Earth is not 70% water

00:00:02.260 --> 00:00:02.960
It never has been

00:00:03.580 --> 00:00:06.520
Only 70% of Earth's surface is covered by water

00:00:07.120 --> 00:00:07.460
By mass

00:00:08.180 --> 00:00:12.500
water makes up just 0.023% of the entire planet

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.900
Almost all of Earth is rock and metal

00:00:15.560 --> 00:00:17.500
The oceans are just a thin layer on top

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:20.340
If you collected every drop of water on Earth

00:00:20.780 --> 00:00:21.280
all oceans

00:00:21.540 --> 00:00:21.880
ice caps

00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:23.140
ground water and clouds

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:26.500
it would barely register compared to the planet beneath it

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:29.340
Now imagine Earth is the size of an apple

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:31.060
The solid planet

00:00:31.480 --> 00:00:31.800
crust

00:00:32.460 --> 00:00:32.780
mantle

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:33.520
core

00:00:33.980 --> 00:00:35.260
is the apple itself

00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:37.620
All the water on Earth

00:00:38.140 --> 00:00:39.620
everything life depends on

00:00:40.040 --> 00:00:41.640
would be thinner than the skin of the

00:00:41.640 --> 00:00:41.920
apple

00:00:42.860 --> 00:00:43.780
A fragile coating

00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:45.740
a microscopic film

00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:47.100
From space

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:49.760
that skin makes Earth look blue and flooded

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:51.220
but in reality

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:52.540
life survives

00:00:52.540 --> 00:00:55.080
on a surface layer so thin it's almost an illusion

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:57.420
Earth isn't a water planet

00:00:57.960 --> 00:01:01.200
it's a massive rock wrapped in a barely there layer that

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:02.760
just happens to keep us alive
